text.tspan: know the constraints of all deployments
know & protect the non- functional risks of the
most demanding users (e.g. perf, capacity, HA)
maintain & action an engineering improvement backlog
conﬁdence to reject PRs for maintainability reasons
help onboard and train new teams & individuals
ensure decision reasons are captured for others to learn from
use corrections as an opportunity to educate contributors
so contributions can get deployed quickly
